      "name": "Demo_Video.txt",
      "content": "This document outlines the demo process for the Real-time Data Pipelines.\n\nVideo Title: AuroraTech ETL Pipeline Operations\nLength: 3-5 minutes\n\nScript / Flow:\n1. Architecture Overview (0:00 - 0:45)\n   - Explain the data sources and Airflow DAG setup.\n\n2. Pipeline Triggering (0:45 - 2:00)\n   - Open Airflow Web UI.\n   - Manually trigger `auroratech_realtime_pipeline`.\n   - Show tasks transitioning: `extract_currency_rates` -> `extract_shipping_logistics` -> `transform_and_load`.\n\n3. Transformation Logic Proof (2:00 - 3:00)\n   - View XCom push details showing component_delay_days and freight costs.\n   - View Logs on `transform_and_load` task to show Ocean-to-Air logic trigger.\n\n4. Destination Validation (3:00 - End)\n   - Connect to Postgres.\n   - `SELECT * FROM dwh.fact_chromebook_margin_risk ORDER BY created_at DESC LIMIT 5;` to prove data insertion.",
      "isBinary": false
